      <intermediateExchange id="6706447b-7e8e-5797-901d-a09759793d06" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" variableName="diclphenol" casNumber="000120-83-2" amount="0.931911738" sourceId="e7f2b25f-57cb-49d4-91e0-794daad01cf9" sourceYear="2005" sourceFirstAuthor="Hischier, R." intermediateExchangeId="f1df8dfc-212e-49a2-bfbc-287dc8eb5da3" activityLinkId="0c2dde9c-0d6d-5f1c-84ee-ce99c518d739">
        <name xml:lang="en">2,4-dichlorophenol</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Approximated processes. This is used to represent 4,4'-Dichlorodiphenylsulfone which is an important substance in the production of polysulfone. Value based on chemical equation for production of 1 kg of polysulfone. A efficiency of 95% is assumed based on Hischier et al. (2005) estimation for chemical production inventory.
n HOC6H4OH + n (ClC6H4)2SO2 + n Na2CO3 -&gt; [OC6H4OC6H4SO2C6H4]n + 2n NaCl + n H2O + n CO2</comment>
